12
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:30,940
You raised me to be a hell of a guinea pig. Thank you, Mother.

13
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,610
What's going on?

14
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:36,750
Quite possibly, he's developed immunity from the previous shot.

15
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:40,300
Still, who knew he'd develop immunity this fast?

16
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:44,170
What are you waiting for? Get him!

17
00:03:03,530 --> 00:03:06,300
If you move even a step,

18
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:10,780
you'll see something horrendous you'll never forget.

19
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:14,320
What are you doing? Grab him now!

20
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:30,860
I'll make sure you get a cozy position for all your cooperation.

21
00:03:31,510 --> 00:03:36,970
What the hell am I doing? Should I turn the car around?

22
00:03:46,130 --> 00:03:48,040
You startled me!

23
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:51,010
Hey, Do Jeong Wu, what are you doing here?

24
00:03:51,010 --> 00:03:55,120
How have you been, Deputy Chief? I missed you.

25
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:58,820
You're one crazy jerk.

26
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:03,540
Aren't you supposed to continue to stay low?  Why show up in front of me?

27
00:04:03,540 --> 00:04:08,390
I fully understand what you did at the autopsy room.

28
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:14,010
Well, about that, I had no choice.

29
00:04:15,210 --> 00:04:19,300
Jeong Wu, are you really the culprit?

30
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:22,610
Will anything change if I'm not the culprit?

31
00:04:22,610 --> 00:04:26,690
I'm going crazy. What's going on here? I haven't a clue.

32
00:04:26,690 --> 00:04:30,230
About the Chief of Staff at the Blue House, Oh Jeong Hwan, the man harassing you.

33
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:35,470
- How do you know about him?
 - He's scheming something big.

34
00:04:35,470 --> 00:04:37,190
What scheme?

35
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:39,270
Something that must be stopped at any cost.

36
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:42,830
I've got to stop it, and I need your help, Deputy Chief.

37
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:51,310
What did you say a minute ago?

38
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:55,920
You said before  that just when you think it's all over, that is when it begins.

39
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:58,250
Apparently, you don't have a full grasp of what's happening here.

40
00:04:58,250 --> 00:05:01,560
Any idea how much money Baegya Foundation has been pouring into the police?

41
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:06,300
