47
00:05:35,570 --> 00:05:38,910
I have two kids who aren't even in college yet.

48
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:44,450
 Confidence in government authority has been compromised.

49
00:05:44,450 --> 00:05:49,350
 I'm not proud of being a police officer anymore.

50
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:55,060
Yes, I shouldn't do anything shameful. I can't let myself be humiliated.

51
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:57,000
Listen carefully.

52
00:05:57,000 --> 00:06:01,440
I've just been informed one of our own is in grave danger in the basement of this structure.

53
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:04,450
Even though we have lost the public's confidence in us,

54
00:06:04,450 --> 00:06:08,010
we, the police cannot let ourselves be intimidated by criminals.

55
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:10,510
That is not right, is it?

56
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:14,660
- What are waiting for? Go and round them up!
 - Yes, sir!

57
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:23,360
You go left!  You go right

58
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,350
I think it's better for us to leave here for now.

59
00:06:25,350 --> 00:06:28,410
Let's go! Move!

60
00:06:40,030 --> 00:06:44,440
I'll see you again soon.

61
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:19,110
I'll be on the lookout here. You go ahead and search!

62
00:07:19,110 --> 00:07:21,040
Move!
 - Yes, sir.

63
