66
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:59,320
I'll give you my jacket. You put it over your head.

67
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:03,340
No one should see me helping out a wanted criminal.

68
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:07,070
I'm fine. But I need help with the guy over there.

69
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:09,370
- Who is he?
 - You don't need to know.

70
00:08:09,370 --> 00:08:12,380
Have you gone mad? You can't tie a man in chains like that.

71
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:17,420
Damn it, how can I undo the chain?

72
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:29,870
How on earth did Do Jeong Wu know and show up in the basement of that structure?

73
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:32,830
I'm not sure, sir.

74
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:44,790
Where are we this time?

75
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:47,060
