78
00:08:55,380 --> 00:08:58,070
Hey, Jeong Wu, are you really going to be okay?

79
00:08:58,070 --> 00:09:02,970
Quit worrying about me. You just be careful. You don't know what Oh Jeong Hwan is up to.

80
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:07,330
