93
00:10:24,860 --> 00:10:28,770
 I think I may be of help.

94
00:10:28,770 --> 00:10:33,180
 I'll bring my computer. I think I can at least find out which hospital you received surgery at.

95
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:35,250
 I won't leave you guys alone.

96
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:39,270
He seemed a completely different person when I saw him again at White Night Village.

97
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:42,320
Dissociative Identity Disorder? You mean multiple personality disorder?

98
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:46,490
Handing him over to the police while he's being dominated by a personality different from the one at the time of the murder,

99
00:10:46,490 --> 00:10:48,840
