102
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:02,670
That's right.

103
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:05,900
Even so, the truth must be revealed.

104
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:11,540
I also had the  amnesia that stemmed from Dissociative Identity Disorder at one point.

105
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:15,310
Apparently, my memory loss was because I'd witnessed the horrendous killing that day.

106
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:18,820
The third child said the same thing.

107
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:25,200
 You guys left me all alone in the dark just to leave and save yourselves..

108
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:28,590
 I won't leave you guys alone.

109
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:34,580
In that sense, all of us became the victims of what happened that day.

110
00:11:36,140 --> 00:11:38,360
Okay, you got me there.

111
00:11:39,410 --> 00:11:44,410
- I'm not saying it's your fault. 
 -  No, I'm right, it was all my fault.

112
00:11:44,410 --> 00:11:46,830
So I'm trying to put things back where they were.

