00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:06,360
 Chief of Staff, Oh Jeong Hwan

116
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:09,010
What a perfect timing!

117
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,030
This is Hwang Byeong Cheol.

118
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:16,920
- What the hell do you think you are doing?
 -  Honey!

119
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:20,230
 How could I have known you'd be there of all places?

120
00:12:20,230 --> 00:12:25,490
If I had, I wouldn't have gone there. I just heard one of my police guys was held in there.

121
00:12:25,490 --> 00:12:28,120
- Where's Do Jeong Wu? 
 - I don't know either.

122
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:33,430
I guess I was wrong thinking that you're a family man.

123
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:41,300
A-Are you threatening me?

124
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:44,390
At any rate,

125
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:48,560
I've just told you what kind of a man I think you are.

126
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:52,540
Let me tell you this. I saw a lot of things I shouldn't have yesterday.

127
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:57,680
I wasn't alone. Many of my guys were there as well.

128
00:12:57,680 --> 00:13:01,310
Anyhow, I'll have them shut their mouths about what they saw.

129
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:05,440
So stop calling me!

130
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,920
Dad!

131
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,370
Dad!

132
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:30,690
Dad, please let me be out.

133
00:13:30,690 --> 00:13:32,790
Where do you want to go?

134
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:42,510
Dad. Dad, please.

135
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:44,220
What are you doing?

136
00:13:44,220 --> 00:13:48,410
Why are you doing this? What do you think you're doing?

137
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:51,410
Oh sweetie!

138
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:55,150
You have a visitor.

139
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:09,710
What on earth is happening?

140
00:14:09,710 --> 00:14:13,660
I safeguarded your life from the third child.

141
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:19,380
However I can't tell when that child will seek you out again.

142
00:14:19,380 --> 00:14:22,050
- Do Jeong Wu took the third child with him. 
 - What?

143
00:14:22,050 --> 00:14:24,420
What?

144
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:26,940
Why are you so surprised? I thought you've known it all along.

145
00:14:26,940 --> 00:14:30,560
I understand you're upset with me because I didn't tell you about the third child.

146
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:33,920
But I know nothing about what's happening now.

147
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:39,010
- You're telling me you aren't a mole. 
 - What reason do I have to be one?

148
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:51,180
I need children.

149
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:55,960
- Children? 
 - Because of Do Jeong Wu, I'm having a hard time getting children for the experiment.

150
00:14:55,960 --> 00:15:00,310
I  need children under the age of fourteen right away.

151
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:10,130
 You said you'd like to be nominated to be on the foundation's board of directors.

152
00:15:10,130 --> 00:15:16,030
What's hanging on the balance isn't a director's position, but the last chance to save your life.

153
00:16:06,610 --> 00:16:08,850
Do you remember Dr. Jo Hyeon Hui?

154
00:16:14,050 --> 00:16:15,880
I do.

155
