160
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:48,250
-  Does that make sense? 
 - Apparently, she tested the formula I created on herself.

161
00:16:48,250 --> 00:16:52,100
Your formula? Was it the reason why she looked so hard for you?

162
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:54,550
I guess it worked.

163
00:16:57,870 --> 00:17:00,700
Where is your formula now?

164
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:03,320
Do you have it?

165
00:17:05,270 --> 00:17:08,040
