166
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:58,940
- Are you okay? 
 - I guess.

167
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,190
Actually, I'm not.

168
00:18:04,190 --> 00:18:07,410
I'm very confused.

169
00:18:07,410 --> 00:18:09,950
About Jo Hyeon Hui being alive?

170
00:18:13,670 --> 00:18:18,220
