171
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:23,830
I thought I wouldn't be too shocked even if I'd meet my birth mother some day.

172
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:28,170
It'll be even more shocking if your birth mom looks the same as before.

173
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:34,220
As I began regaining my memory,

174
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:36,660
