As I've believed all along, you're the role model of the Korean police force.

201
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:34,610
- Thank you, sir! 
 - Got it already. Let go. Come on now.

202
00:20:34,610 --> 00:20:37,560
- You crazy jerks. 
 - Thank you, sir!

