I failed to acknowledge your hard work all this time, and that was my mistake.

489
00:52:27,550 --> 00:52:31,060
And His Excellency scolded me a lot for that.

490
00:52:32,020 --> 00:52:34,910
I am sorry about that.

491
00:52:34,910 --> 00:52:39,500
You don't have to apologize to me.

492
00:52:40,940 --> 00:52:43,970
You can go ahead and leave work now. I'm going to see His...

493
00:53:52,050 --> 00:53:54,190
Please go in.

494
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:32,190
This place...

495
00:54:42,610 --> 00:54:48,270
I saved the Guinea pig.  Now only the fourth child is left.

496
00:55:39,400 --> 00:55:43,250
I devoted everything to you. But this is how it is, in the end?

497
00:55:43,250 --> 00:55:46,090
You are a rat born to be experimented on.

498
00:55:46,090 --> 00:55:48,790
But I fed you, gave you shelter, and even gave you money.

499
00:55:48,790 --> 00:55:52,400
I let you live as a human being until now, isn't that enough?

500
00:55:53,530 --> 00:55:56,360
Do Jeong Wu was right.

501
00:55:56,360 --> 00:56:01,560
And now, do you need my serum, too?

502
00:56:04,470 --> 00:56:09,240
So it was you, you damned bastard.

503
00:56:09,240 --> 00:56:12,560
Since you know it, things should finish up easily.

504
00:56:52,160 --> 00:56:55,290
Let's take care of this quickly and go.

505
00:56:55,290 --> 00:57:00,840
Do you really think I can be captured that easily?

506
00:57:00,840 --> 00:57:03,780
I guess you have someone you trust.

507
00:57:03,780 --> 00:57:07,530
Of course there is some one.

508
00:57:14,480 --> 00:57:19,920
What's this place? This is not the secret laboratory.

509
00:57:21,850 --> 00:57:27,340
 When I survived White Night Village, I resented the person who made the village that way.

510
00:57:27,340 --> 00:57:32,540
 I didn't think about what me and the other children suffered there.

511
00:57:32,540 --> 00:57:36,140
 When I felt my life was ruined, Oh Jeong Hwan appeared.

512
00:57:36,140 --> 00:57:39,340
 He took me in when I didn't have the will to live.

513
00:57:39,340 --> 00:57:43,970
 So I pledged loyalty and my remaining life to him.

514
00:57:43,970 --> 00:57:45,450
 And?

515
00:57:45,450 --> 00:57:47,860
 Then you appeared.

516
00:57:56,280 --> 00:58:00,870
 Shoot me with a tranquilizer gun so that Oh Jeong Hwan doesn't notice.

517
00:58:02,610 --> 00:58:06,390
 I've already developed an immunity to it, so it won't be effective.

518
00:58:23,560 --> 00:58:26,540
So will you be monitoring me forever now?

519
00:58:26,540 --> 00:58:29,430
Nothing is eternal in this world.

520
00:58:32,200 --> 00:58:35,420
 Program Installing

521
00:58:36,840 --> 00:58:40,650
You shouldn't treat him like an object after using him as your hands and feet all of his life.

522
00:58:40,650 --> 00:58:42,310
I am not treating him like an object.

523
00:58:42,310 --> 00:58:44,840
Just retrieving my test subject.

524
00:58:44,840 --> 00:58:50,430
That's very nice and all, but what is such a high-ranking person doing in such a dark and remote place?

525
00:58:50,430 --> 00:58:54,680
And just you two? What if something happens to you?

526
00:58:54,680 --> 00:58:56,510
Are you worrying for my sake now?

527
00:58:56,510 --> 00:59:00,240
I'm not worrying. It was just tough to come all this way.

528
00:59:00,240 --> 00:59:05,100
And I already worked so hard looking for His Excellency. So I was annoyed.

529
00:59:05,100 --> 00:59:08,800
So, after all that work, did you find him?

530
00:59:08,800 --> 00:59:10,410
His Excellency?

531
00:59:10,410 --> 00:59:12,500
I did.

532
00:59:15,240 --> 00:59:20,110
You are right in front me, Your Excellency.

533
00:59:34,920 --> 00:59:41,990

534
01:00:03,040 --> 01:00:05,770
 Awaken

535
01:00:05,770 --> 01:00:07,660
 I made a deal with Do Jeong Wu.

536
01:00:07,660 --> 01:00:11,460
 You sacrificed so many children to make this medicine?

537
01:00:11,460 --> 01:00:12,970
 To try and live forever?

538
01:00:12,970 --> 01:00:13,910
 Mom.

539
01:00:13,910 --> 01:00:16,490
 You grew up well, my daughter.

540
01:00:16,490 --> 01:00:19,530
 Stop saying useless things and return Dr. Jamie.

541
01:00:19,530 --> 01:00:22,110
 - Oppa!
 - Team Leader!

542
01:00:22,110 --> 01:00:25,080
 The two of us have to disappear for this sad story to end.

543
01:00:25,080 --> 01:00:26,490
 No, don't do it.

544
01:00:26,490 --> 01:00:29,910
 You were born for this purpose.

545
01:00:29,910 --> 01:00:33,470
 My... monster.
